description: “She thinks the ring is being resized & won’t be here for a few more weeks,” he told me. She wanted engagement pictures & didn’t mind that the ring wouldn’t be in the photos. Little did she know, he had the ring in hand & was ready to get down on one knee! The weather was a magnificent 72 degrees, the sun was setting just behind the trees, the ring fit stunningly, and the look on her face was something out of a movie. I may or may not have been crying the whole time I was taking photos. “It’s fine, THERE’S SOMETHING IN MY EYE!!”
